  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">To build capacities of peoples and their organisations on human rights engagement from community, local, and national levels.

Seminars on human rights will be held in target areas raising the awareness and capacity of people&#x2019;s organisations to assert and defend their collective rights. Case stories showcasing the assertion and defense of these rights by people&#x2019;s organisations will support this effort. The seminars will include formulation of a people&#x2019;s engagement strategy to raise people&#x2019;s rights issues at various levels. An interface between people&#x2019;s organizations and local government officials and concerned agencies aims to improve engagement climate among development actors on the basis of human rights-based approaches and instruments.</narrative>
  </description>
